  + [finding_002] is the candidate route still needs a selection rule for the active cylinder
    = meaning: scale invariance alone does not say which cylinder carries Theta control, pressure decomposition, and epsilon-smallness together
  + [finding_003] is pressure decomposition must be same-frame
